OpenVPN is a full-featured open source SSL VPN solution
that accommodates a wide range of configurations, including
remote access, site-to-site VPNs, Wi-Fi security, and
enterprise-scale remote access solutions with load 
balancing, failover, and fine-grained access-controls.
Starting with the fundamental premise that complexity
is the enemy of security, OpenVPN offers a cost-effective,
lightweight alternative to other VPN technologies that is 
well-targeted for the SME and enterprise markets.